<\f[B]p\f[R] id=\[dq]myRandText\[dq]>The random numbers are:</\f[B]p\f[R]>
<\f[B]button\f[R] type=\[dq]button\[dq] onClick=\[dq]genRandomNumbers()\[dq]>
